'''热带风暴乔吉特'''（{{lang-en|Tropical Storm Georgette}}）是2010年9月吹袭[[南下加利福尼亚州|南下加利福尼亚州]]的一场持续时间较短的热带风暴，于9月20日经东[[太平洋|太平洋]]上空的[[热带扰动|扰动天气区]]发展成型。次日，气旋在南下加利福尼亚州以南近海升级成热带风暴。乔吉特经过[[下加利福尼亚半岛|下加利福尼亚半岛]]并减弱成热带低气压，然后继续北上，于9月22日[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]墨西哥本土，最终于次日清晨在[[索诺拉州|索诺拉州]]内陆上空消散。

虽然气象机构发布警告，称墨西哥西北部及下加利福尼亚半岛可能会降下暴雨，但该国的受灾程度很轻，也没有出现人员丧生。不过，气旋的残留湿气之后进入[[新墨西哥州|新墨西哥州]]，引发的洪灾夺走一条人命。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Georgette 2010 track.png}}
9月1目，一股[[东风波|东风波]]离开非洲西海岸向西穿越[[大西洋|大西洋盆地]]，在此期间因组织混乱而难以追踪。9月7日东风波逼近[[小安的列斯群岛|小安的列斯群岛]]时，其中的[[对流|对流]]已有增长。9月14日，东风波北部在西[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]发展成[[2010年飓风卡尔|飓风卡尔]]，南部则穿越[[中美洲|中美洲]]北部，于9月17日进入东[[太平洋|太平洋]]。<ref name="TCR">{{cite report | author = Michael J. Brennan | publisher = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | date = 2010-11-04 | accessdate = 2016-10-12 | title = Tropical Storm Georgette Tropical Cyclone Report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/EP122010_Georgette.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305134526/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/EP122010_Georgette.pdf | format = [[便携式文档格式|PDF]] | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | deadurl = no }}</ref>[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]此时首度在热带天气展望中提及这片扰动天气区存在，但没有预计系统会出现显著发展<ref name="TWO">{{cite report | title = Tropical Weather Outllook | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-10-12 | author = Todd Kimberlain | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/epac/201009181751/index.php?basin=epac&current_issuance=201009181751 | deadurl = no | date = 2010-09-18 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304093843/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/epac/201009181751/index.php?basin=epac&current_issuance=201009181751 }}</ref>。不过，该机构在下一份热带天气展望中指出，天气系统所在海域的[[风切变|风切变]]会略有减弱，所以扰动天气有中等程度可能会在之后48小时内发展成[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]<ref name="TWO2">{{cite report | publisher = National Hurricane Center | author = John Cangialosi | title = Tropical Weather Outlook (2) | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304215926/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/epac/201009192344/index.php?basin=epac&current_issuance=201009192344 | accessdate = 2016-10-12 | date = 2010-08-19 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/epac/201009192344/index.php?basin=epac&current_issuance=201009192344 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

系统在[[索诺拉州|索诺拉州]]以西洋面逐渐发展，对流围绕[[大气环流|环流中心]]聚拢。9月20日下午，系统内发展出[[低气压|低气压区]]，促使美国国家飓风中心将位于[[卡波圣卢卡斯|卡波圣卢卡斯]]（{{lang|en|Cabo San Lucas}}）[[罗盘方位|东南偏南]]方向约390公里海域的天气系统归类成热带低气压。气旋位于[[副热带高压脊|副热带高压脊]]的西部边缘，自始至终都在其影响下转西北偏北方向移动。<ref name="TCR" />

9月20日当天，气旋在成为热带低气压仅数小时后就因强烈风切变影响导致对流消亡。但从[[散射仪|ASCAT散射仪]]的数据来看，系统的风速已达到烈风强度，热带低气压因此在[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]9月21日凌晨0点升级成热带风暴。<ref name="TCR" />美国国家飓风中心在当时的实际操作中直到{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}这天中午12点才发布针对风暴的首份公告，并以“乔吉特”（{{lang|en|Georgette}}）为其命名。在此期间，气旋中心附近的雷暴活动有所增长。<ref>{{cite report | author = Robbie Berg | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2010-09-21 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160317164423/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/ep12/ep122010.discus.001.shtml | accessdate = 2016-10-12 | title = Tropical Storm Georgette Discussion One | archivedate = 2016-03-17 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/ep12/ep122010.discus.001.shtml? }}</ref>9月21日，风暴逼近[[南下加利福尼亚州|南下加利福尼亚州]]，其强度和前进方向都没有什么变化。{{lang|en|UTC}}下午18点左右，乔吉特以[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]65公里强度从圣荷西卡波（{{lang|en|San José del Cabo}}）附近[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]，气象部门还测得999[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，29.5[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）气压值。进入[[加利福尼亚湾|加利福尼亚湾]]后不久，乔吉特减弱成热带低气压，风速保持在每小时55公里。气旋接下来又从圣卡洛斯（{{lang|en|San Carlos}}）附近登陆[[索诺拉州|索诺拉州]]。进入内陆上空后不久，乔吉特的下层环流便在墨西哥西部山区上空消散。<ref name="TCR" />

== 防灾措施和影响 ==
[[File:Georgette_2010_rainfall.gif|thumb]]
墨西哥政府在风暴来袭前向南下加利福尼亚州最南端地区发布[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴警告]]<ref name="ADV 3" />，但在乔吉特登陆后中止生效<ref name="TCR" />。政府部门向该州乡村地区发出警告，希望当地居民做好应对狂风暴雨的准备<ref name="NCS">{{cite news | title = Alerta BCS por tormenta Georgette | author = Tercer Sistema | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161012091324/http://www.tercersistema.com/2010/09/alerta-bcs-por-tormenta-georgette.html | url = http://www.tercersistema.com/2010/09/alerta-bcs-por-tormenta-georgette.html | publisher = III Sistema rosarito tijuana | accessdate = 2016-10-12 | date = 2010-09-21 | archivedate = 2016-10-12 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。美国国家飓风中心指出，气旋可能产生高达250毫米雨量，特别是高原地区降水可能特别多，引发致命的洪灾和[[泥石流|泥石流]]<ref name="ADV 3">{{cite report | title = Tropical Storm Georgette Public Advisory 3 | author = John Brown | date = 2010-09-21 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160317165231/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/ep12/ep122010.public.003.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/ep12/ep122010.public.003.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-17 | access-date = 2016-10-12 }}</ref>。政府官员在[[洛斯卡沃斯|洛斯卡沃斯]]开设有四个避难所，并将洪水易发地区的上千户居民疏散<ref>{{cite news | title = La tormenta tropical Georgette impacta la tarde de hoy en La Paz | accessdate = 2016-10-12 | url = http://www.cronica.com.mx/notas/2010/533376.html | author = PEDRO JUáREZ MEJíA | archivedate = 2016-10-12 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161012092043/http://www.cronica.com.mx/notas/2010/533376.html | date = 2010-09-22 | publisher = La Crónica Diaria S.A. de C.V. }}</ref>。

索诺拉州民防部门下令该州南部进入“橙色”警戒状态<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Reza | first1 = Francisco | title = Amenaza "Georgette" con lluvias al Sur | url = http://www.elimparcial.com/EdicionEnLinea/Notas/Noticias/22092010/469724.aspx | accessdate = 2012-03-04 | newspaper = El Imparcial | date = 2010-09-22 | author2 = Gerardo López | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120304191145/http://www.elimparcial.com/EdicionEnLinea/Notas/Noticias/22092010/469724.aspx | location = Hermosillo | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2012-03-04 }}</ref>，此后不久又升级成“红色”警戒，乔吉特当晚登陆后，上述警戒停止生效<ref name="Georgette alert lifted">{{cite news | last = Ojeda | first = Yesicka | title = Levantan alerta por "Georgette" en Guaymas y Empalme | accessdate = 2014-02-22 | newspaper = El Imparcial | date = 2010-09-22 | url = http://www.elimparcial.com/EdicionEnLinea/Notas/Noticias/22092010/469899.aspx | location = Hermosillo | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140222193655/http://www.elimparcial.com/EdicionEnLinea/Notas/Noticias/22092010/469899.aspx | archivedate = 2014-02-22 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。卡加米（{{lang|en|Cajeme}}）一共开设有52个避难所<ref>{{cite news | last = López | first = Eduardo | title = Hay calma en Cajeme por "Georgette" | url = http://www.elimparcial.com/EdicionEnLinea/Notas/Noticias/22092010/469856.aspx | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2014-02-28 | newspaper = El Imparcial | date = 2010-09-22 | location = Hermosillo | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140228161135/http://www.elimparcial.com/EdicionEnLinea/Notas/Noticias/22092010/469856.aspx | archivedate = 2014-02-28 }}</ref>。[[瓜伊马斯|瓜伊马斯]]及其周边地区有300人进入避难所，[[恩帕尔梅_(索诺拉州)|恩帕尔梅]]（{{lang|en|Empalme}}）也有250人<ref>{{cite news | last = Reza | first = Francisco | title = Albergan refugios a decenas en Guaymas y Empalme | url = http://www.elimparcial.com/EdicionEnLinea/Notas/Noticias/22092010/469832.aspx | accessdate = 2012-03-04 | newspaper = El Imparcial | date = 2010-09-22 | location = Hermosillo | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120304191001/http://www.elimparcial.com/EdicionEnLinea/Notas/Noticias/22092010/469832.aspx | archivedate = 2012-03-04 }}</ref>。[[巴希亚基诺|巴希亚基诺]]（{{lang|en|Bahía Kino}}）和[[埃莫西约|埃莫西约]]沿海地区的学校停课，以防万一<ref>{{cite news | last = Zepeda | first = Ana Isabel | title = Suspenden clases en Costa de Hermosillo | archivedate = 2014-02-28 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140228235221/http://www.elimparcial.com/EdicionEnLinea/Notas/Noticias/22092010/469835.aspx | url = http://www.elimparcial.com/EdicionEnLinea/Notas/Noticias/22092010/469835.aspx | accessdate = 2014-02-28 | newspaper = El Imparcial | date = 2010-09-22 | location = Hermosillo }}</ref>。9月23日，州内学校开课<ref>{{cite news | last = Zepeda | first = Ana Isabel | title = Vuelven hoy a clases más de 612 mil alumnos | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140228010054/http://www.elimparcial.com/EdicionEnLinea/Notas/Noticias/23092010/469935.aspx | url = http://www.elimparcial.com/EdicionEnLinea/Notas/Noticias/23092010/469935.aspx | accessdate = 2014-02-28 | newspaper = El Imparcial | date = 2010-09-22 | location = Hermosillo | archivedate = 2014-02-28 }}</ref>。

乔吉特在南下加利福尼亚州产生的降雨量创下15年来新高，导致许多人流离失所<ref name="heaviest rain">{{cite news | title = Mexico hit by Tropical Storm Georgette | accessdate = 2016-10-12 | publisher = Breaking Travel News | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140221173415/http://www.breakingtravelnews.com/news/article/mexico-hit-by-tropical-storm-georgette/ | url = http://www.breakingtravelnews.com/news/article/mexico-hit-by-tropical-storm-georgette/ | date = 2010-07-23 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-02-21 }}</ref>。风暴还产生大浪，数天前[[2010年飓风卡尔|飓风卡尔]]登陆墨西哥后已引发洪灾，乔吉特的到来又令情况雪上加霜<ref name="BBC">{{cite news | title = Tropical storm brings fresh flood misery to Mexico | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/world-latin-america-11386824 | publisher = BBC News | accessdate = 2016-10-12 | date = 2011-08-04 | archive-date = 2021-01-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210107040620/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-latin-america-11386824 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。托多斯桑托斯（{{lang|en|Todos Santos}}）的降雨量最高，达到150毫米<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/georgette2010filledrainblk.gif | date = 2010-10-21 | title = Tropical Storm Georgette | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | author = David M. Roth | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304130850/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/georgette2010filledrainblk.gif | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | accessdate = 2016-10-12 }}</ref>。索诺拉州多地降下120毫米雨量，引发的洪灾令220套民房受损<ref>{{cite news | author = Ulises Gutiérrez, Javier Valdez, Sergio Ocampo, Julia Le Duc, David Carrizales, Agustín Galo, Octavio Vélez, René Alberto López, Luis A. Boffil y Notimex | publisher = La Jordana | date = 2010-09-23 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120228225047/http://www.revistaasi.com.mx/vernoticias.php?artids=2577&categoria=25 | accessdate = 2012-02-28 | title = Graves daños en varias zonas de Sonora, tras intensas lluvias | archivedate = 2012-02-28 | url = http://www.revistaasi.com.mx/vernoticias.php?artids=2577&categoria=25 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。气旋在瓜伊马斯产生66毫米降水<ref name="Georgette alert lifted" />。恩帕尔梅、瓜伊马斯、伊查荷亚（{{lang|en|Etchojoa}}）[[纳沃华|纳沃华]]和[[洛斯莫奇斯|洛斯莫奇斯]]爆发洪灾，50万人被迫疏散<ref name="TCR" />。降水产生大量地表径流，诺维洛水库的进水速度达每秒510立方米，迫使有关部门开闸放水<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Ojeda | first1 = Yesika | title = Deja "Georgette" agua a Sonora | accessdate = 2014-09-23 | newspaper = El Imparcial | date = 2010-09-23 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140222190645/http://www.elimparcial.com/EdicionEnLinea/Notas/Noticias/23092010/469933.aspx | url = http://www.elimparcial.com/EdicionEnLinea/Notas/Noticias/23092010/469933.aspx | author2 = Francisco Reza | location = Hermosillo | archivedate = 2014-02-22 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。

乔吉特的残留水分与逐渐逼近的低压槽结合，令新墨西哥州普降暴雨并伴有强烈雷暴。[[犹尼昂县_(新墨西哥州)|犹尼昂县]]测得163毫米雨量。<ref>{{cite web |date=2010-12-31 |title=A Recipe for Heavy Rain - September 22, 2010 |publisher=Albuquerque, New Mexico National Weather Service |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120805234332/http://www.srh.noaa.gov/abq/?n=climonhigh2010sepsigevents |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2012-08-05 |url=http://www.srh.noaa.gov/abq/?n=climonhigh2010sepsigevents |archivedate=2012-08-05 }}</ref>降雨引发洪灾，导致[[格兰德河|格兰德河]]位于[[伯纳利欧县|伯纳利欧县]][[卡努尔_(新墨西哥州)|卡努尔]]（{{lang|en|Carnuel}}）境内河段沿线有一人丧生<ref>{{cite journal | volume = 55 | number = 9 | title = Storm Data and Unusual Weather Phenomena with Late Reports and Corrections | date = 2010-09 | publisher = National Climatic Data Center | accessdate = 2016-10-12 | deadurl = yes | issn = 0039-1972 | archivedate = 2016-10-12 | editor1 = Joseph E. Kraft | editor2 = Rhonda Herndon | url = http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS/IPS-0D959391-5093-4B2F-8912-68B86531DA6D.pdf | format = PDF | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161012144323/http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS/IPS-6D6D0466-A706-4481-AA98-5016C894E966.pdf | journal =  }}[http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/IPS/sd/sd.html 此网站] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/IPS/sd/sd.html |date=20160414065723 }}可查询美国国家海洋和大气管理局风暴数据平面出版物的内容，但查询结果链接有效时间仅有24小时，用户可选择“2010-9”获得所需要的信息。</ref>。

